# Ignore filled character sheets
# Pattern: [CharacterName]_Character_Sheet.[ext]
# Examples: Thorin_Ironforge_Character_Sheet.pdf, Aria_Moonwhisper_Character_Sheet.xlsx

# Ignore all character sheets EXCEPT Blank_
*Character_Sheet.pdf
*Character_Sheet.xlsx
*Character_Sheet.docx

# But keep the blank templates
!Blank_Character_Sheet.pdf
!Blank_Character_Sheet.xlsx
!Blank_Character_Sheet.docx

# Ignore temporary files
*.tmp
*.temp
~$*.docx
